{
  "id": "69febad79a77bdc777cf4745",
  "title": "任天堂法務部は別に最強ではない",
  "created": 1778301656,
  "updated": 1778338869,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69febad79a77bdc777cf4745",
      "text": "任天堂法務部は別に最強ではない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad70000000000910295",
      "text": "from [任天堂法務部]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad70000000000910296",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301661
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad70000000000910297",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad70000000000910298",
      "text": "[https://www.minpokyo.org/incident/2024/12/10622/ 任天堂における紹介予定派遣のパワハラ・直接雇用拒否事件～大阪高裁判決のご報告～ | 民主法律協会（民法協）]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad70000000000910299",
      "text": " 任天堂法務部、[パワハラ問題]で労働者相手に負ける",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad7000000000091029a",
      "text": " \tこの事件で、この企業の部署は訴訟される側となると都市伝説的な強さはないなと気づいた[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad7000000000091029b",
      "text": " \t\tあったらそれはそれで困るが",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad7000000000091029c",
      "text": " \t\tする・されるの区分で勝率が変わってるわけではないと思う[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad7000000000091029d",
      "text": " \t\t\t著作物に関する訴訟の強さが話題になるだけで",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad7000000000091029e",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t確かに[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad7000000000091029f",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t[撤回.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102a0",
      "text": " \tというか、労働者を抑圧する側の[企業法務]を無節操に持ち上げたり、茶化したりするのは良くないと思う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102a1",
      "text": " \t\tいつも任天堂法務部を称賛する任天堂ファン(の一部)はこの事件に一切触れなかったけど何故なんだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102a2",
      "text": " \t\tそもそも[任天堂]はジャニーズを最高裁判決後もCM起用してたし、社会的にかなり不味い組織なのは確か",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102a3",
      "text": " \t\t\t客層的に子供相手の商売でもあるのに、司法(と[NYTimes])公認の[チャイルド・マレスター]系企業をわざわざ広告に使うというのは常軌を逸している",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102a4",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t公共組織を除けば、[ドラゼミ]という幼児教室を展開していた[ドラえもん]が映画でジャニーズを声優として起用したことの次に不味い起用だと思っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102a5",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t[児童性的虐待]を支援したと思われてもまあ無理もない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102a6",
      "text": " [https://www.axios.com/2022/10/13/nintendo-settles-labor-union-mackenzie-clifton Nintendo settles labor dispute over unions with game tester MacKenzie Clifton]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102a7",
      "text": " \tアメリカの事例だけど、これも相当にまずい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102a8",
      "text": " \t\tしかもこっちも普通に負けてるし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102a9",
      "text": " \t\t\t[常勝無敗]では全然ないのは確か",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102aa",
      "text": " \t[労組潰し]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102ab",
      "text": "\t \t[組合潰し]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102ac",
      "text": " \t[https://www.axios.com/2022/09/29/nintendo-tester-union-busting-whistleblower Exclusive: Fired Nintendo worker speaks out, alleging union-busting]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febc4700000000009102e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778302024,
      "updated": 1778302024
    },
    {
      "id": "69febba000000000009102e4",
      "text": "✂ [最強法務の戦場違い]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301857,
      "updated": 1778301962
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102c0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301656
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb7500000000009102e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301814,
      "updated": 1778301814
    },
    {
      "id": "69febad700000000009102c1",
      "text": "[法曹界内の「強さ」]は分かるものなのだろうか……。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301656,
      "updated": 1778301742
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb1900000000009102db",
      "text": "\tあるいは、[法曹界内の「強さ」]の話として最強が使われているのだろうか。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301722,
      "updated": 1778301722
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb4700000000009102e1",
      "text": " \t[法曹界内の「強さ」]で言えば[任天堂]みたいな企業の[法務部]ではなく、[国家機関]が最強だと思う。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301768,
      "updated": 1778301768
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb3400000000009102e0",
      "text": " \t\t✂ [法曹界内の「強さ」は分かるものなのだろうか]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301749,
      "updated": 1778301769
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb1900000000009102dc",
      "text": "\t私（[Summer498.icon]）は[ゲーム業界]や[エンタメ]の[知財]の[法務部]の中で最強とかくらいに読んでた。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301722,
      "updated": 1778301749
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb4f00000000009102e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301777,
      "updated": 1778301942
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff485000000000000b6cdb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778337873,
      "updated": 1778337873
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff485000000000000b6cdc",
      "text": "件の事件は 1審京都地裁、2審大阪高裁っぽい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778337873,
      "updated": 1778337936
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff489000000000000b6cde",
      "text": "\t[https://www.e-sanro.net/share/pdf/magazine/con-roudouhanrei-2024.pdf 労働判例―人事労務に活かす判例実務誌 No.1318 2024.12.15]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778337936,
      "updated": 1778338418
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff4a0700000000000b6ce1",
      "text": "  京都地裁 令和6年2月27日判決",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778338312,
      "updated": 1778338427
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff4a7a00000000000b6ce4",
      "text": "  判例検索で京都地裁で同日に判決された労働に関する裁判が1件見つかる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778338427,
      "updated": 1778338637
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff4a2800000000000b6ce2",
      "text": "   [https://www.courts.go.jp/hanrei/search1/index.html 裁判例検索 | 裁判所]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778338344,
      "updated": 1778338499
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff4ac400000000000b6ce5",
      "text": "  [労働弁護団通信の記事 https://roudou-bengodan.com/wpRB/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/通信366号.pdf]と照らし合わせると、この1件が当該事件かどうか判断できる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778338501,
      "updated": 1778338869
    },
    {
      "id": "69ff485500000000000b6cdd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778337878,
      "updated": 1778337878
    }
  ]
}